## ğŸŒŸ Features
- **Mirror Mode:** Quick appearance check directly on your wrist display.  
- **Appearance AI:** Outfit color matching, grooming tips, and style insights.  
- **Posture & Fitness Sync:** Uses motion sensors and AI to track habits that affect how you look.  
- **Lookbook Mode:** Save and rate your daily looks privately.  
- **AI Voice Explainer:** Embedded TTS demo that walks through the product idea.

